e.DEFAULT_INSTANCE`.\n- Kept the `ExtensionRegistryLiteTest` focused on the active class and its reflective delegation path.\n- Kept `protobuf-java` as `testCompileOnly` plus existing `testRuntimeOnly`, so the new test can compile against `Extension`/`ExtensionRegistry` while preserving runtime availability.\n\nFiles updated:\n- `tests/src/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-javalite/3.25.3/src/test/java/com_google_protobuf/protobuf_javalite/GeneratedMessageLiteInnerSerializedFormTest.java`\n- `tests/src/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-javalite/3.25.3/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/reachability-metadata.json`\n- `tests/src/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-javalite/3.25.3/build.gradle`\n- `tests/src/com.google.protobuf/protobuf-javalite/3.25.3/src/test/java/com_google_protobuf/protobuf_javalite/ExtensionRegistryLiteTest.java`\n\nI did not run the Gradle command locally, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01d30a87a98476de0169f8f4ba8eec819f870e8067c44537c8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 343, "output": 1257, "cacheRead": 52224, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53824, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777923243346, "responseId": "resp_01d30a87a98476de0169f8f4ac665c819f966a280081a1ad85"}, "toolResults": []}
